						<p>Same wall.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Tribhº Kulōttuṅga-chōḷadēva: Year 3+1st = 1152-53 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription records the gift of one <hi rend="italic">sandhyā</hi> lamp to the deity Avināśi Āḷuḍaiyār and an endowment of some <hi rend="italic">Paḻañjalākai achchu</hi> to provide for burning the lamp by Marudanmalaiyaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Kulōttuṅgachōḻa-Vikkiramādittadēvan, a <hi rend="italic">sāmanta</hi> (feudatory) of the king.</p>						

